'''Adam Smith''' ({{Azmez n talalit|5|yunyu|1723}} - {{Azmez n tamettant|17|yulyu|1790}}) d [[afelsuf]] dɣa [[adamsan]] [[Tagelda Yeddukklen|abriṭani]] n [[Tufawin tikusiyin|Tufawin]]. Yeqqim deg umezruy am baba-s n [[tussna tudmist]] tatrart, ayɣef amahil agejdan, ''[[Inadiyen ɣef agama d tisebbiwin n tabaɣurt n iɣlanen|Tabaɣurt n iɣlanen]]'', d yiwen n iḍrisen imesbedden n [[alellamẓri udmis|ulellamẓri udmis]]. Aselmad n [[tafelsuft tazerfant]] di [[tasdawit n Glasgow]], yefka-d mraw iseggwasen n tameddurt-is i uḍris agi yehregen idemsanen imeqranen uḍfiren, widak [[Karl Marx]] yetsemmi « [[agaru akelsak|ikelsaken]] » dɣa ad ersen imenzayen imeqranen n [[alellamẓri udmis]].


Aṭas n medden ssnen Adam Smith asmi yura yiwen udlis g useggwas n  1776 umi qqaren Wealth of Nations ([[Ayla n Iɣlanen]]); d bab n weḍru n tikta n talellamt (libéralisme). 

==Ayen yura Adam Smith==

*The Theory of Moral Sentiments (1759) 
*An Inquiry into the Nature and Causes of the Wealth of Nations (1776)

